joxy.border

Class JoxyTitledBorder

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.border.AbstractBorder
      • javax.swing.border.TitledBorder
        • joxy.border.JoxyTitledBorder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Border

    public class JoxyTitledBorder
extends TitledBorder
    This class implements a more KDE-like variant of the TitledBorder. It looks more like a KDE GroupBox.

    We try to substitute Joxy-specific borders for the default Java Swing borders in the JoxyPanelUI class.

    Author:
    Thom Castermans, Willem Sonke
    See Also:
